.SH NAME
.PP
madlang \- a text templating language for generative literature
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
madlang run <file>
.PP
madlang tree <file>
.PP
madlang check <file>
.PP
madlang get <repo>
.PP
madlang sample <repo>
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\f[B]madlang\f[] is an interpreted language for generative literature
and computational creativity.
